{"word":"G4873 - συνανάκειμαι - synanákeimai - soon-an-ak'-i-mahee - Sit with","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συνανάκειμαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">synanákeimai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soon-an-ak'-i-mahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Sit with</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கூடப்பந்தியிரு, கூடயிரு"},{"paragraph":"to recline together, feast together"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G345 - ἀνακεῖμαι - anakeîmai - an-ak-i'-mahee/345\">G345</a>; to <i>recline</i> in company <i>with</i> (at a meal): - sit (down, at the table, together) with (at meat).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1945/1945\">G1945</a>, <a href=\"#/G2621/2621\">G2621</a>, <a href=\"#/G2749/2749\">G2749</a>, <a href=\"#/G345/345\">G345</a>, <a href=\"#/G3873/3873\">G3873</a>, <a href=\"#/G4029/4029\">G4029</a>, <a href=\"#/G4295/4295\">G4295</a>, <a href=\"#/G480/480\">G480</a>, <a href=\"#/G4873/4873\">G4873</a>, <a href=\"#/G606/606\">G606</a>"}]}